IgnoreAlphaTest (Material stage keyword)
========================================

Description
-----------

This particular keyword prevents the global effect of the [alphaTest](AlphaTest\_(Material\_stage\_keyword)) stage keyword from being applied to the current stage.

Usage
-----

`ignoreAlphaTest`

Parameters
----------

This keyword does not accept parameters.

Example
-------

`textures/modwiki/exIgnoreAlphaTest {`
`  DECAL_MACRO`
`  noshadows`
`  noselfshadow`
`  {`
`    blend diffusemap`
`    map textures/learning/tst3.tga`
`    alphaTest 0.5`
`  }`
`  {`
`    blend add`
`    map textures/decals/blood_drip1`
`    ignoreAlphaTest`
`  }`
`}`

Notes
-----

To elaborate: [alphaTest](AlphaTest\_(Material\_stage\_keyword)) is a stage specific keyword (i.e. it can only be put in a certain stage, never in the global section) but it has an effect on all stages. So, ignoreAlphaTest disables this effect on the stages where it is specified.


